Package: snpscope
Maintainer: Jeffrey Bhasin <jeffb@case.edu>
Author: Jeffrey Bhasin <jeffb@case.edu>
Version: 0.1
License: GPL-3
Title: snpscope: Compute overlap of SNPs with regulatory elements and export to CSV or the UCSC Genome Browser
Description: Uses shiny to launch a web-based interface to select SNPs and regulatory elements and allows downloading a CSV of element overlaps and provides visualization by creating a UCSC genome browser session using rtracklayer.
Depends:
    shiny,
    rtracklayer,
    NCBI2R,
    stringr,
    reshape,
    plyr
Suggests:
    testthat,
    roxygen2
Collate:
    'snpscope-package.r'
    'snpscope.r'
